This paper discusses security and privacy concerns related to cloud-based solutions, which falls under the category of "Computer Security and Cryptography" (cs.CR). The paper also proposes a framework that leverages edge computing to enable user-centric search on encrypted big data, which involves distributed computing (cs.DC) and database management (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the development of a prototype system, which involves software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper addresses privacy concerns, which falls under the category of "Computers and Society" (cs.CY).
